      • doAcquireLock

        public static boolean doAcquireLock(redis.clients.jedis.Jedis jedis,
                                    String namespace,
                                    String lockName,
                                    String lockHolder,
                                    int timeout)
        Helper method that encapsulates the logic to acquire a lock.
        Parameters:
        jedis - the connection to Redis
        namespace - the Resque namespace
        lockName - all calls to this method will contend for a unique lock with the name of lockName
        timeout - seconds until the lock will expire
        lockHolder - a unique string used to tell if you are the current holder of a lock for both acquisition, and extension
        Returns:
        Whether or not the lock was acquired.
